## Sequoia v0.1.0

Sequoia is installed and active. It provides multi-agent code auditing with 9 specialized agents (6 phase agents + 2 meta-agents + 1 orchestrator).

### Available Commands

| Command | Description |
|---------|-------------|
| `/sequoia init` | Initialize Sequoia in the current project. Builds the Project Map. Run first. |
| `/sequoia audit` | Full technical audit — all agents in parallel, then correlation and scoring. |
| `/sequoia review` | Focused review of changed files. Faster than audit, deeper than a linter. |
| `/sequoia fix` | Generate actionable tasks from the latest audit findings. |
| `/sequoia diff` | Compare current state against the last recorded audit. |

### Quick Start

```
/sequoia init          # always first
/sequoia audit         # full audit
/sequoia audit --phase=security --mode=quick   # quick security scan
/sequoia review --pr=42    # review a PR
```

### Agent Coverage

P1 Security · P2 Performance · P3 Architecture · P4 Quality · P5 Experience · P6 Operations
M1 Correlator · M2 Reporter · C0 Orchestrator

The skill is at `~/.gemini/sequoia/skills/SKILL.md`. The orchestrator (C0) coordinates all agents and synthesizes findings into a Health Score (0–100).
